vestock.%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22numb_20_9%22%20bk%3D%22numb%22%20ch%3D%2220%22%20vn%3D%229%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E9%3C%2Fspan%3ESo%20Moses%20did%20as%20he%20was%20told.%20He%20took%20the%20staff%20from%20the%20place%20where%20it%20was%20kept%20before%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22numb_20_10%22%20bk%3D%22numb%22%20ch%3D%2220%22%20vn%3D%2210%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E10%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20he%20and%20Aaron%20summoned%20the%20people%20to%20come%20and%20gather%20at%20the%20rock.%20%26%23x201C%3BListen%2C%20you%20rebels!%26%23x201D%3B%20he%20shouted.%20%26%23x201C%3BMust%20we%20bring%20you%20water%20from%20this%20rock%3F%26%23x201D%3B%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22numb_20_11%22%20bk%3D%22numb%22%20ch%3D%2220%22%20vn%3D%2211%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E11%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20Moses%20raised%20his%20hand%20and%20struck%20the%20rock%20twice%20with%20the%20staff%2C%20and%20water%20gushed%20out.%20So%20the%20entire%20community%20and%20their%20livestock%20drank%20their%20fill.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22numb_20_12%22%20bk%3D%22numb%22%20ch%3D%2220%22%20vn%3D%2212%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E12%3C%2Fspan%3EBut%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20said%20to%20Moses%20and%20Aaron%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BBecause%20you%20did%20not%20trust%20me%20enough%20to%20demonstrate%20my%20holiness%20to%20the%20people%20of%20Israel%2C%20you%20will%20not%20lead%20them%20into%20the%20land%20I%20am%20giving%20them!%26%23x201D%3B%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22numb_20_13%22%20bk%3D%22numb%22%20ch%3D%2220%22%20vn%3D%2213%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E13%3C%2Fspan%3EThis%20place%20was%20known%20as%20the%20waters%20of%20Meribah%20(which%20means%20%26%23x201C%3